hopobject.body: How long are you planning to stay here? unimed clinicas credenciadas sp A lot has gone wrong for the Jets over the past 10 years, but even had they been managed better and coached better and played better, they still had to go up against the Patriots of Belichick and Brady, one of the greatest football dynasties in the history of the sport, whether the Giants clipped them a couple of times in Super Bowls or not.
